fields.Title: WHIRLING F2 / DREAM 4
fields.Description: Dream in which you are the world-detector.

fields.Title: START
input
You: "Spinning on empty."
fields.Dialogue Text: Spinning on empty.

fields.Title: You: "Why?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Why?

fields.Title: You: "Forget politics. I'll never sleep i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Forget politics. I'll never sleep if I keep on like this.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "No. You're spinning tapes at the di..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No. You're spinning tapes at the discotheque. The great, unceasing disco of the mind. The flash! The bang! The endless *learning* experience.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "You'll go insane if you keep going..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You'll go insane if you keep going like this. One more day and you'll be in the loonie bin. I just know you will. And for what, brother-man?

fields.Title: Shivers: "Do it for the wind."
fields.Dialogue Text: Do it for the wind.

fields.Title: You: "[Open your eyes.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Open your eyes.]

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Just another thoughtless vessel plo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Just another thoughtless vessel ploughing the grey seas of the everyday.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Thoughts, baby. A million little li..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Thoughts, baby. A million little lights in the dark. You're one fine instrument, brother -- all those faces and all those names, all that laughter and screaming and scheming around... Every corner and every street...

fields.Title: You: "I can't give up. I have to keep goi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I can't give up. I have to keep going, for Revachol... [Pursue thought.]

fields.Title: You: "We're making progress. Measured, st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: We're making progress. Measured, steady progress... [Pursue thought.]

fields.Title: Limbic System: "There he goes again. He's a real po..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There he goes again. He's a real political animal, our Harry. He still doesn't see that it's the world that's changing *him*...

fields.Title: Jump to: [Limbic System: "Beep-beep-beep! The alarm is ringin..."]
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "You're the son of the World again...."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're the son of the World again. Harrister -- a ceaseless agent picking up litter and old newspapers, collecting your little bubble gum wrappers and idiotic picture post cards. Meaningless, meaningless keepsakes.

fields.Title: You: "I'm just looking out for my economi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm just looking out for my economic self-interest... [Pursue thought.]

IsTHCPresent("revacholian_nationhood")
!(IsTHCPresent("revacholian_nationhood"))
Empathy: "For the greater good."
fields.Dialogue Text: For the greater good.

fields.Title: Endurance: "For Revachol. Always and only Revac..."
fields.Dialogue Text: For Revachol. Always and only Revachol.

fields.Title: You: "Spinning in eternity."
fields.Dialogue Text: Spinning in eternity.

fields.Title: You: "But what if I want to be the agent..."
fields.Dialogue Text: But what if I want to be the agent of nothing?

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Beep-beep-beep! The alarm is ringin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Beep-beep-beep! The alarm is ringing, Harry. The disco circus goes on and on! You barely slept three hours last night.

fields.Title: Jump to: [lastdreamhub]
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "It's the *world*, Harry-boy. And yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's the *world*, Harry-boy. And you're *made* of it. Every day you're out there you make more of yourself from it. I'm afraid you can't be *unmade* now.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "You can never forget this shit."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can never forget this shit.

fields.Title: IsTHCPresent("moralist")
IsTHCPresent("moralist")
!(IsTHCPresent("moralist"))
You: "You're right. It's time to get poli..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You're right. It's time to get political.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "It's not possible anymore. It's *st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's not possible anymore. It's *stuck* on loop... Whirling, spitting out words and images.

fields.Title: Logic: "Do it for the picture puzzle. Put i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Do it for the picture puzzle. Put it all together. Solve the world. One conversation at a time.

fields.Title: IsTHCPresent("communist")
IsTHCPresent("communist")
!(IsTHCPresent("communist"))
You: "Yes, I'm sure. I am very boring and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes, I'm sure. I am very boring and *apolitical* and sleepy. [Ignore thought.]

fields.Title: Savoir Faire: "For the money, baby."
fields.Dialogue Text: For the money, baby.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Recorded in you. Forever. On ferrot..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Recorded in you. Forever. On ferrotape.

fields.Title: You: "The colours. The voices."
fields.Dialogue Text: The colours. The voices.

fields.Title: politihub
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "Are you sure? You could be closing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Are you sure? You could be closing the door on a brilliant and *special* future for yourself.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Coz only love can break your heart...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Coz only love can break your heart...

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "I knew you couldn't resist. So now..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I knew you couldn't resist. So now you're gonna change the world, but how?

fields.Title: You: "*What* is it?"
fields.Dialogue Text: *What* is it?

fields.Title: You: "The rain, the snow... I don't want..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The rain, the snow... I don't want to. It's beautiful.

fields.Title: You: "The endless visions. Erase them."
fields.Dialogue Text: The endless visions. Erase them.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Beautiful? It's *stuck* on loop......"
fields.Dialogue Text: Beautiful? It's *stuck* on loop... whirling, spitting out words and images.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "All *stuck* on loop... Whirling, sp..."
fields.Dialogue Text: All *stuck* on loop... Whirling, spitting out words and images.

fields.Title: You: "Feel the pillow under your cheek."
fields.Dialogue Text: Feel the pillow under your cheek.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "He's got no idea what he's in for."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's got no idea what he's in for.

fields.Title: Ancient Reptilian Brain: "On and on it goes, for untold hours..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On and on it goes, for untold hours. At the disco where you first asked her to dance. Rising -- rising! -- above the dark curvature. The great wingspan of sleep, studded with stars.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Reading your awful letters and *rec..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Reading your awful letters and *recalling* things, aren't you? The endless names of the world... An address book, you are. The map of a city.

fields.Title: You: "Spinning, spinning... tell me, am I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Spinning, spinning... tell me, am I dreaming?

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Behold, there are *millions* of the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Behold, there are *millions* of them down there. The first time. The last time. The smoke in her mouth, the potted flowers, the faces: turning, changing.

fields.Title: Limbic System: "Solving your little crossword puzzl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Solving your little crossword puzzles? Doing your tasks, crossing names off your lists? Trying to become some sort of world-detector... It won't make it *okay*. It won't put smoke back in her mouth...

fields.Title: You: "I'm building communism for all. Thi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm building communism for all. This time we won't fail... [Pursue thought.]

fields.Title: You: "That's right. I *am* an agent of th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: That's right. I *am* an agent of the world.

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "For the working class."
fields.Dialogue Text: For the working class.

IsTHCPresent("ultraliberal")

Jump to: [politihub]
Ancient Reptilian Brain: "It's too late. You're not *made* of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's too late. You're not *made* of nothing anymore, you're something now, Harry. I tried to drown you in the black water but you re-emerged. Kicking and screaming. Running. And for what?

fields.Title: Volition: "You can do it. It's nothing. Do it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can do it. It's nothing. Do it for the city. Go.
